OL,3,CPolls close in Makerfield by-election
OL,5,FPolls have closed in the Makerfield
OL,6,Fconstituency - set to be one of the
OL,7,Fmost consequential by-elections in
OL,8,FBritish political history.
OL,10,FFourteen candidates stood for the
OL,11,Fseat, which became vacant after
OL,12,FLabour's Josh Simons resigned.
OL,14,FLabour's candidate in the Greater
OL,15,FManchester constituency, Andy Burnham,
OL,16,Fis hoping to return to Parliament to
OL,17,Freplace Sir Keir Starmer as prime
OL,18,Fminister if he wins.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
