OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1781857089
OL,3,CPolls close in Makerfield by-election
OL,5,FAhead of polling, he urged people to
OL,6,F"vote to change politics" and vowed to
OL,7,Ftake the "fight as high as I can
OL,8,Fpossibly take it".
OL,10,FStarmer has said he was willing to
OL,11,Foffer the Mayor of Greater Manchester
OL,12,Fa "big" job in his government, should
OL,13,FBurnham win.
OL,15,FBut Burnham has since confirmed he
OL,16,Fwill not be taking any government role
OL,17,Fthat may be offered to him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
